lead_paragraph: Sen. Ted Cruz on Saturday continued his call for cutting off funding for President Barack Obama's health care law and told conservative Christians that congressional lawmakers can't be counted on to do it.

headline.main: Cruz Again Raps Obama's Health Care Law
headline.print_headline: Cruz Again Raps Obama's Health Care Law
